In this directory, we have input.txt and input_bdg_bulk.txt

script run assumes executable floquet is a symbolic link to executable in src directory.

Example readin files are shown here (for time-independent problem, PMAX=0):
-- input.txt --
Hamiltonian     bdg
topology        bulk

-- input_bdg_bulk.txt --
PMAX    0
NKX     201

h       1.2
mu      0.2
T       25.0
Delta0  0.5
v       1.2

kmax    5
chern   connection

-- or --
PMAX    0
NKX     201

h       1.2
mu      0.2
T       25.0
Delta0  0.5
v       1.2

kmax    5
chern   curvature



